  "texts": [
    "Entries in the audit trail are time-stamped, and the citizen either requests the entire audit trail, or a snippet for a particular time interval.",
    "Upon a citizen query, the secure world digitally signs and sends the audit trail.",
    "The citizen then uses the audit trail as follows:1 Check normal world OS/ROS2/SROS integrity.",
    "The citizen first uses the attestation report to verify the integrity of the normal world OS, ROS2, and SROS.",
    "This step is critical because Pd-Ros relies on the normal world OS to ensure that access to the camera hardware is restricted to a single application."
  ],
